---
title: Carb Smart Soy Marinated Turkey with Sesame Dressed Greens
description: Fire up the broiler and set the table. Tonight's sticky sweet soy marinated turkey will have your mouth watering. Paired with perfectly charred peppers, toasted peanuts and sesame-dressed greens, your plate will be clean in no time!

